<solution>
<p><ul><li>3.9987729889544</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={900}{e}^{{{0.19}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{1924}={900}{e}^{{{0.19}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{1924}}{{900}}={e}^{{{0.19}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{1924}}{{900}}\right)}}}={0.19}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{1924}}{{900}}\right)}}}}{{0.19}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={3.9987729889544}</m></p>
</solution>
